### Search: Empty Query (Should Fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/   
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
}


### Search: Very Long Query (Should Fail if >500 chars)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/this is a very long search query that goes on and on and on and continues for a very long time with many words and phrases and technical terms and concepts and ideas that keep going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and going and beyond the maximum allowed length
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
}


### Search: Missing Authorization (Should Fail - 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/test query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
}


### Search: Missing UserId (Should Fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/test query
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{}


### Search: Invalid UserId Format (Should Fail - 400 Validation Error)
# This tests that invalid userId formats are caught by Zod validation
# Expected: 400 Bad Request with validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/test query
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{
  "userId": "invalid-user-id-with-spaces-and-special-chars!"
}


### Search: Unauthorized Access Attempt (Should Fail - 403 Forbidden)
# This tests that users cannot access other users' data
# Expected: 403 Forbidden - Authorization denied
# NOTE: Change "DIFFERENT_USER_ID_HERE" to a valid but different user ID to test
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/test query
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{
  "userId": "kDcDxFooqlNggViiihoYJr8TWdA2"
}


