GET {{baseUrl}}/list/{{testUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Get Bookmarks: Invalid UserId Format (Should Fail - 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/list/invalid user id!
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}


### Get Bookmarks: Non-existent User (Should Return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/list/nonExistentUser99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}


